### Backend Logic & Security (Controllers)

#### [MODIFY] [backend/middleware/auth.js](file:///c:/Users/justi/Downloads/School%20Files/MainProjectCollection/ComprogStudies/ProjectsWebDev/Capstone%20Things/DeveloperVersion/backend/middleware/auth.js)
- Update the JWT token generation to include the user's `branchId`.
- When verifying the token, attach `req.user.branchId` to the request so all routes know which branch is asking for data.

#### [MODIFY] [backend/controllers/jobController.js](file:///c:/Users/justi/Downloads/School%20Files/MainProjectCollection/ComprogStudies/ProjectsWebDev/Capstone%20Things/DeveloperVersion/backend/controllers/jobController.js)
- **`getJobs`:** Update the query to filter by branch: `Job.find({ branchId: req.user.branchId })`. This prevents the "South" branch from seeing "Main" branch cars.
- **`createJob`:** Automatically assign the incoming job to the branch of the Service Advisor who created it (`newJob.branchId = req.user.branchId`).

